This is where champions are forged ‚Äî every drop, rotation, and clutch matters. With ‚Çπ 50 lakh on the line and the pride of representing the region on LAN, only the best will survive the storm.

snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Created by: Raj & DK

Directed by: Raj & DK, Suman Kumar, Tusshar Seyth
Produced by: Raj & DK
Written by Suman Kumar, Raj & DK
Screenplays by: Suman Kumar, Raj & DK, Sudhish Kamath, Nikhil Gonsalves  
Dialogues: Sumit Arora

Associate Producer: Anuradha Sharma

Associate Director: Chesta Goswami

Director Of Photography: Jay Charola
Production Designer: Parichit Paralkar

Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81516058

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

snippet.title: Michael | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
MICHAEL - in cinemas soon.
____ 
Michael is the cinematic portrayal of the life and legacy of one of the most influential artists the world has ever known.
 
The film tells the story of Michael Jackson‚Äôs life beyond the music, tracing his journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world.
 
Highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career, the film gives audiences a front-row seat to Michael Jackson as never before. This is where his story begins.
 
Michael stars Jaafar Jackson in his feature film debut, Nia Long (Empire, The Best Man franchise), Laura Harrier (BlacKkKlansman, Spider-Man: Homecoming) and Juliano Krue Valdi (The Loud House, Arco), with Miles Teller (Top Gun: Maverick, Whiplash) and two-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee Colman Domingo (Sing Sing, Rustin).
 
Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy Award¬Æ winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

Directed by Antoine Fuqua, the award-winning filmmaker of Training Day, Olympus Has Fallen and The Equalizer franchise, from a screenplay by three-time Academy Award¬Æ nominee John Logan (Gladiator, The Aviator), the film is produced by Academy Award¬Æ winner Graham King (The Departed, Bohemian Rhapsody), John Branca (executive producer This Is It, Thriller 40) and John McClain (executive producer This Is It, Michael Jackson Live at Wembley July 16, 1988).

snippet.title: Dil Kya Kare Jab Kisi Ko (Lyric Video) - Julie | Kishore Kumar
snippet.description:
‚ÄúDil Kya Kare Jab Kisi Ko‚Äù is one of the most soulful romantic songs from the 1975 film Julie. Sung in the golden voice of Kishore Kumar, the music is composed by the legendary Rajesh Roshan, with heartfelt lyrics penned by Anand Bakshi. This evergreen melody beautifully captures the emotions of love and longing, making it one of the most cherished classics of Hindi cinema. 

Credits: 
Singer: Kishore Kumar
Music: Rajesh Roshan
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 
 Oonchi-oonchi diwaaron si 
 Is duniya ki rasmein 
 Ho na kuch tere bas mein Julie 
 Na kuch mere bas mein 
 Dil kya kare jab kisi se 
 Kisi ko pyar ho jaaye 
 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 

Jaise parwat pe ghata jhukti hai

 Jaane kahan kab kisi ko 
 Kisi se pyar ho jaaye 

 Aa main teri yaad mein sab ko bhula doon

Presenting new Haryanvi hip hop 2025 ‚Äì Matter by Sumit Parta & Panther

Bringing you the raw and fearless vibe of Haryana with "Matter", the latest fire track by Sumit Parta & Panther.
This song defines real street energy ‚Äî filled with power, attitude, and pride. With intense lyrics, bold delivery, and unstoppable flow, Matter is all about dominance, loyalty, and living with no compromise.

If you believe in your hustle and never back down ‚Äî this one‚Äôs for you.

Par Yaari Dosti Me Koni Roli Chalya Kre 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
 Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya  Kre 

Bair Mhare Chori Sun Dada Layi Chalre H
Gelya Chacha Tau Aale Mere Bhai Chalre H 
Kayi Sale Mere Laan Ki Sakeem Sochre H 
Anty Party Te  Krn Collab Pochre H 

Phle Karam Kand Krya Ib Bnya Hu Me  Singer 
Choro Jaata Ko  Sage Bishnoiya Ka Tinger 
Adhe Shise Khule Bhar Kade Rakhe Chora Finger
5,7 Bhai Paad Dewa Karwayi 
Konya Krke Yo Chora Kathi Toli Chalya Krya 
Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre 

Ye Ghoda Chalta Bhi Aur Jalta Bhi
Bas Bhaagta Bhagataa Lekin Peecha Hat-ta Nahi
Ye Ghoda Jeet Dilata Aur Karta Barbaadi
Deta Nahi Maafi Hai Karta Sardari
Aur Faadein Beech Se Gar Bane Koi Jyada Patwari

Raub Jamata Ye Gaddafi Nahi Jhukta Bhale Hi Katta Sir
Mujhe Gaddari Dikhe Minute Se Pehle Got The Vision Of Gandhari
Hoti Mahabharat Tune Buri Nazar Se Dekh Li Gar Meri Panchali
Tere Chacha Bappa Sabki Karwadu Baikunth Tayyari
Aur Sun
Kam Se Jyaada Hai Zubaan Ki Izzat
Aukat Se Jyaada Karte Iman Ki Izzat
Chadhai Se Jyaada Ache Insan Ki
Hum Bhaukal Se Zyaada Karte Ache Khandan Ki Izzat
Gunday Badmash Company Me Jaise Ye Yashraj Ki Picture
Pakke Usool, Lathi Hai Har Sanp Ki Ksimat
Naseeb Me Bheji Bhagwan Ne Pehli Ashiqui Likh Kar
Aur Duji Maut Seene Pe Goli Hath Me Pistol

Hoti Pitayi Lage Kohli Mara Kare
Judge Sab Bole Galat Karam Pe Tere Moti Dhara Lage
Khatey Bikaneri Na Goli Guli Khaya Kare
Panther Bhaiya Jaha Phonchey Og Og Nara Lage

Mkha Kaan Khol Dhyan Te Tu Baat Sun Chooti 
Badmasha Ki Re Koi Prem Khani Konya Hoti 
Tane Mare Subha Shyam Fer  Bole Ga Re Gaam 
Gundya Gelya Link H Flane Ki H Poti 
Karke Ne Kand Kde Bhaje Koni Yaar 
Mhari Sadka Pe Gadi Ye Slowly Chalya Kre 

Jiki Nasa Me Se Pani Woye Kre Samjhota 
Mhare Matter  Me Sun Sidhi Goli Chalya Kre



Stay Tuned & Subscribe/Follow me on:

* Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sumitparta09/

snippet.title: NZ vs WI | 3rd T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
snippet.description:
New Zealand won the third T20I against the West Indies by 9 runs in a match played on November 9, 2025, at Saxton Oval in Nelson. The victory gives New Zealand a 2-1 lead in the five-match series. New Zealand batted first and posted a total of 177 for 9. West Indies made a strong late comeback but fell short of the target in the final over, scoring 168 runs.

snippet.title: Mehrama - (Extended) Audio Lyrical | Love Aaj Kal | Kartik | Sara | Pritam | Darshan Raval | Antara
snippet.description:
Feel the soft and emotional vibe of Mehrama. Sung by Darshan Raval and Antara Mitra, this song gently reminds us of love and memories.

#mehrama #loveaajkal #darshanraval #antaramitra #pritam #kartikaaryan #saraalikhan #romantichindisongs #bollywoodsongs #hindisong #romanticsong #irshadkamil 

Credits:
Song: Mehrama Extended
Movie - Love Aaj Kal
Song - Mehrama 
Music - Pritam
Singers - Darshan Raval & Antara Mitra
Lyrics - Irshad Kamil

Lyrics:
Chahiye kisi saaye mein jagah
Chaaha bahut baar hai
Na kahin kabhi mera dil laga
Kaisa samajhdaar hai

Main na ponhchoon kyu wahan pe
Jaana chaahoon main jahaan
Main kahaan kho gaya
Aisa kya ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Na khabar apni rahi
Na khabar apni rahi
Na raha tera pata

Oh meharma kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Jo shor ka hissa hui
Woh aawaz hoon
Logon mein hoon
Par tanha hoon main
Haan tanha hoon main

Duniya mujhe mujhse juda hi karti rahe
Bolun magar na baatein karun
Yeh kya hoon main

Sab hai lekin main nahin hoon
Woh jo thoda tha sahi
Woh hawaa ho gaya
Kyu khafa ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Yun to yeh jahan paa liya
Maine hi mujhe paaya na
Hoke auron saa jaane kyun
Jeena hi mujhe aaya na

Duniya main itna uljha
Khud se main toota hoon
Mujhse hamesha main hi peeche chhoota

Main kahan kho gaya
Aisa kya ho gaya

Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
Oh mehrama kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata

Na khabar apni rahi
Na khabar apni rahi
Na raha tera pata
Oh meherma kya mila
Yun juda hoke bata
